<br>
It's a minor pet peeve, but another thing that really pisses me off i ssomething like this:<br>
<br>
We are doing a LDoN.  Tough mobs (we aren't the uber motherfuckers that can solo this place ... some people still PLAY this game, thank you) are taking time to kill, but we are doing ok overall.  Suddenly, some whiney little zit-scar says something like this:<br>
&quot;OMG we aer only have 35 minutes left!!!  OMG We aer teh gonna FAIL!!&quot;<br>
<br>
OK, lets look at this.<br>
First, the 30 points you will get for this adventure is NOT that big of a deal!  Much more important is the MASSIVE XP/AA ground you are able to cover in a VERY short time, the HUGE amounts of money you make in a very short time (comparitively speaking) and the skills of team work and creative use of your class you may be able to pick up.  I have ben in groups that were good going in, nd by the time we finished, we were fucking ROCKING.  If we did another one, we fucking KICKED ASS!  My average is about half and half, and for a gimp SK like me, thats pretty good.  Fail?  WHO FUCKING CARES!  It's about 30 god damn points... seriously ... most of the worth a shit items are in the upper hundreds ... so is 30 points THAT big a deal?  FUCKING CHILL !!! DAMN !<br>
<br>
Second point... If you are watching your timer as you wring your hands thinking &quot;OMG OMG OMG OMG We aer teh suck&quot; you are NOT watching your group and concentrating on your work.  Hey healer ... how about a GOD DAMN HEAL !!!<br>
... yeah, I Know ... revolutionary idea.<br>
<br>
Third point ... by stressing over your time limits, you are making other people nervous and inviting a wipeout.  I have been in groups that WOULD have won, but some shit-burger got all stressed out and got the entire group scared (Oh noZ ... we might not get out 30 points ... NOOOOz!!!one11) and stupid mistakes got us wiped out.  <br>
<br>
If you are so god damn worried about completing the adventure, STAY FOCUSED!!!  If nothing else, you might JUST LEARN YOUR FUCKING CLASS and make yourself a better player for it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=toraria>Toraria</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#330000>(11/14/03 8:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1136.topic&index=53>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Game related Peeve's and annoyance's</span><hr size=1> Ninja SoE<br>
